<div><head>筆經一卷</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.2">漢時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.3">諸邵獻兔毫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.4">出鴻都，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.5">惟有趙國毫中用。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.6">時人咸言：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.7">兔毫無優劣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.8">管手有巧拙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.9">有人以綠沉漆竹管，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.10">及鏤管見遺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.11">錄之多年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.12">斯亦可愛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-1a.13">玩詎必金寶彫琢然後為寶也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.2">昔人或以瑠璃象牙為筆管，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.3">麗飾則有之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.4">然筆須輕便，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.5">重則躓矣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.6">諸郡毫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.7">惟中山兔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.8">肥而毫長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.9">可用。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.10">先用人髮杪數十莖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.11">襍青羊毛并兔毳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.12">裁令齊平，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.13">以麻紙裏枝根令淨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.14">次取上毫薄薄布柱上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-2a.15">令柱不見。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.2">世傳張芝、鍾繇用鼠鬚筆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.3">筆鋒勁強有鋒芒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.4">余未之信，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.5">鼠鬚用未必能佳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.6">甚難得。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.7">嶺外少兔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.8">以雞毛作筆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-3a.9">亦妙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a.2">蜀中石鼠毛可以為筆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a.3">其名曰𪕞。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a.4">人鬚作筆甚佳。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a.5">漢製天子筆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-4a.6">以錯寶為跗。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.2">晉武賜張華麟角筆管。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.3">製筆之法，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.4">桀者居前，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.5">毳者居後。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.6">強者為刃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.7">要者為輔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.8">參之以檾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.9">朿之以管，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.10">固以漆液，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.11">澤以海藻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.12">濡墨而試。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.13">直中繩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.14">勾中鉤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.15">方圓中矩規，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.16">終日握而不敗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1648_CHANT_001-5a.17">故曰筆妙。<lb/></seg>
</p>
